ED_Title: Report of the International  Court of Justice
ED_DecisionText: At its 31st plenary meeting, on 30 October 2024, the General Assembly took note of the report of the International Court of Justice. (Footnote: A/79/4.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/79/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
